title: Youth unemployment rate in Jordan in 2019
summary: In general Youth unemployment rate has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Youth unemployment rate, about 32.62 was reported at Year 2002
The lowest Youth unemployment rate, of value 28.43 was reported at Year 2014
